      "content": "okay i hear you. i'm just really stressed out. he's also been coughing a lot, like a really deep wet cough. i was thinking maybe i could give him some of my own adult ibuprofen too along with the tylenol to make sure it hits from both sides? would that be okay if i just give him a small amount of mine?",
